fixed the form with two key changes:

  1. Added hx-trigger="submit" - Explicitly tells HTMX to handle the form submission event
  2. Changed to this.reset() - Simpler and more reliable way to clear the form after submission

  The form will now:
  - Intercept the submit event with HTMX
  - POST to /askesis/submit-message
  - Append the response to #conversation-messages
  - Reset the form fields automatically
